Permission - Enum in co.kruzr.bernoulli

PermissionDisabledPolicy - Enum in co.kruzr.bernoulli
Covers what to do in the event of a particular Permission being disabled.
permissionName - Variable in enum co.kruzr.bernoulli.Permission
 
PermissionRequestCode - Annotation Type in co.kruzr.bernoulli.annotation
An annotation that specifies the permission request code to be used by a method which has at least one RequiresPermission annotation with a PermissionDisabledPolicy of PermissionDisabledPolicy.ASK_IF_MISSING.
